00:03:43.255 --> 00:03:44.637
the same slope.

00:03:44.637 --> 00:03:45.425
But let's make sure they don't have

00:03:45.425 --> 00:03:47.352
the same y intercept,
and I wouldn't do this

00:03:47.352 --> 00:03:48.989
if I was under time pressure,

00:03:48.989 --> 00:03:50.917
but just for it to feel good about it,

00:03:50.917 --> 00:03:53.435
if this y intercept is six over a,

00:03:53.435 --> 00:03:57.805
so it's going to be six over 28 over nine,

00:04:00.725 --> 00:04:01.882
dividing by a fraction is the same thing

00:04:01.882 --> 00:04:03.414
