00:04:03.414 --> 00:04:04.179
so it's going to be the same thing

00:04:04.179 --> 00:04:07.511
as six times nine over 28,

00:04:07.511 --> 00:04:10.820
and this is going to be
equal to six times nine

00:04:10.820 --> 00:04:14.633
