00:04:14.633 --> 00:04:16.153
which is clearly different

00:04:16.153 --> 00:04:18.255
than three over 14.

00:04:18.255 --> 00:04:20.936
So if a is 28 over nine, same slope,

00:04:20.936 --> 00:04:22.456
different y intercepts,

00:04:22.456 --> 00:04:24.291
and you're dealing with parallel lines,

00:04:24.291 --> 00:04:25.638
